#: ../../source/cookbook/classification.rst:7
msgid "With this recipe, SEPAL will help users build a supervised classification of any mosaic image. It is built on top of the most advanced tools available on Google Earth Engine (including the classifiers CART, RandomForest, NaiveBayes and SVM), allowing users to create an easy-to-use user interface to:"
