#: ../../source/cookbook/classification.rst:16
msgid "Start"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cookbook/classification.rst:18
msgid "Once the classification recipe is selected, SEPAL will show the recipe process in a new tab (1) and the image selection window will appear on the lower-right side (2)."
