#: ../../source/cookbook/classification.rst:367
msgid "The process is nearly the same as found in the documentation above discussing csv tables. The only difference should be the geometry column, as GEE assets usually embed a :code:`.goejson` column by default. If this column exists, it will be autodetected by SEPAL."
